near the west bank town of jenin where 18yearold yussef mohammed 
damaj died of a gunshot wound to the chest the haaretz daily said 
soldiers opened fire as youths hurled rocks at the troops in a 
clash that lasted several hours the newspaper said 
the army confirmed that a dead palestinian was brought to a 
nearby hospital after a clash at the camp but a spokesman said 
soldiers were investigating the cause of death 
damajs death raised to 242 the number of palestinians killed 
